_olex2_refinement_description
;
1. Fixed Uiso
 At 1.2 times of:
  All C(H) groups
 At 1.5 times of:
  All C(H,H,H) groups
2.a Aromatic/amide H refined with riding coordinates:
 C006(H006), C008(H008), C00A(H00A), C00D(H00D), C00E(H00E), C00F(H00F),
 C00G(H00G), C00H(H00H), C00I(H00I), C00K(H00K), C00M(H00M)
2.b Idealised Me refined as rotating group:
 C00N(H00B,H00C,H00J)
;
